  "texts": [
    "For both GPT chatbots, we train the GPT-4 LM on customized data from a small experimental factory in a CSV format.",
    "The offline version is more data secure as the loaded data in its platform remains internal in a local server.",
    "It is not exposed to the web, while data is available to OpenAI on the online model.",
    "The offline version strictly responds to classic information in the loaded factory file.",
    "Since it is directly connected to the robust GPT4-LM database, the online version provides more information and guidance beyond requested prompts and is suitable for operators' knowledge growth and training.Regarding human well-being, we integrate the maximum overtime working hours in the production process to ensure operators are not overworked while producing."
